cily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001553_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001553.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001553-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text checked against photograph in Vento\u003C/span>\u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 1\">line.1: \u003Cspan>Gabrici: ΙΘΙΟΚΑΣΙΑ ΗΡΥΣΑ ΑΓΑΘΑ; Manni Piraino: Ἰθι[. .]ασία ἥρ[υ]σα ἀγαθά\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2> translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>Photograph in Vento is excellent and it is possible to see traces of almost the entire text, as originally read by Gabrici. \u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 50.0993 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 42.1845 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 04.0043 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Kretschmer 1927 307 no.4 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002533\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002533\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Gabrici 1929 55-56 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001976\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001976\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Bisi 1970 101 no.5 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002148\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002148\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manni Piraino 1973 23 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000531\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000531\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Vento 2000 88-91 tav.53-55 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001525\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001525\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">\u003Cp>Simple letters with slight serfis to the strokes, particularly to the top of the alpha. Alpha is broad with straight bar. The initial theta appears circular with a central point; the final theta has a detached horizontal bar and is slightly ovoid.\u003C/p> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence \u003C/div>",[264,267,270,273,276,279,282,285],{"id":265,"html":266},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa, Jonathan Prag\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>Ἰθι\u003Cspan class=\"underline\">ο\u003C/span>κασία ἥρυ̣σα ἀγαθά \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa, Jonathan Prag\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003